*Customer Table*  

| Column Name | Data Type    | Key   | Constraints              | Description                         |
| ----------- | ------------ | ----- | ------------------------ | ----------------------------------- |
| CustomerID  | INT          |  PK   | NOT NULL, AUTO_INCREMENT | Unique identifier for each customer |
| FirstName   | VARCHAR(50)  |       | NOT NULL                 | Customer first name                 |
| LastName    | VARCHAR(50)  |       | NOT NULL                 | Customer last name                  |
| Email       | VARCHAR(100) |       | UNIQUE, NOT NULL         | Customer email for contact          |
| Phone       | VARCHAR(15)  |       |                          | Customer phone number               |

          
*Order Table*
| Column Name | Data Type     | Key   | Constraints                     | Description                      |
| ----------- | ------------- | ----- | ------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| OrderID     | INT           |  PK   | NOT NULL, AUTO_INCREMENT        | Unique identifier for each order |
| CustomerID  | INT           |  FK   | NOT NULL â†’ Customer(CustomerID) | Customer who placed the order    |
| OrderDate   | DATE          |       | NOT NULL                        | Date when the order was placed   |
| TotalAmount | DECIMAL(10,2) |       | NOT NULL                        | Total amount of the order        |

*Product Table*
| Column Name | Data Type     | Key   | Constraints                     | Description                    |
| ----------- | ------------- | ----- | ------------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| ProductID   | INT           |  PK   | NOT NULL, AUTO_INCREMENT        | Unique identifier for product  |
| Name        | VARCHAR(100)  |       | NOT NULL                        | Product name                   |
| Description | TEXT          |       |                                 | Product description            |
| UnitPrice   | DECIMAL(10,2) |       | NOT NULL                        | Price per unit                 |
| SupplierID  | INT           |  FK | NOT NULL â†’ Supplier(SupplierID) | Supplier providing the product   |

